---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const page_title = "Privacy Policy";
const page_description = "Privacy notice for users of privacy-crypto.com.";
---

<Layout title={page_title} description={page_description} maxWidth="max-w-3xl" lang="en">
  <header class="mb-8 border-b border-white/[0.05] pb-6">
    <h1 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-4 text-white">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-slate-400 text-lg leading-relaxed">Last updated: May 2026</p>
  </header>

  <div class="prose prose-invert prose-slate max-w-none">
    <div class="bento-card p-6 border border-white/[0.05] bg-white/[0.02]">
        <p class="text-slate-300 mb-4">
            In compliance with Data Protection regulations, this page outlines how we handle information within this website.
        </p>
        
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-6 mb-3">1. Data Collected</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 mb-4">
            As a static website with an educational purpose, <strong>we do not actively collect personal data</strong>. We do not offer registration forms, nor newsletters that require email addresses. We use anonymized statistical analysis tools (such as Umami Analytics) that do not uniquely track individuals and do not use intrusive tracking cookies.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-6 mb-3">2. Cookies and Tracking</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 mb-4">
            For complete details on cookies used for technical and aggregate statistical purposes, please refer to our <a href="/en/cookie-policy/" class="text-[#0066FF] hover:underline">Cookie Policy</a>.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-6 mb-3">3. Purpose of Data Processing</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 mb-4">
            The technical data collected (e.g., page views, device type) is used solely for aggregate visit measurement and optimization of the user experience on the site.
        </p>

        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-8 italic">
            Note: This notice is provided for transparency purposes. If you desire the highest level of privacy, we always encourage you to browse using anonymity protection tools such as no-log VPNs or Tor networks.
        </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
